# 루트를 build context 로 쓸 때(예: services/usage-service/Dockerfile) 전송 크기 축소
.git
**/.git
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/coverage
**/.turbo
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/build
**/.gradle
**/dist
**/out
**/target
**/*.iml
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log
.cursor
# Monorepo `docker build` context is the repo root, so nested `services/*/web/.dockerignore` is not applied.
# Host-only Next env (e.g. USAGE_WEB_INTERNAL_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3001) must not reach `next build` or
# rewrite destinations are baked as localhost and proxy fails inside containers (ECONNREFUSED to :3001).
**/.env.local
# apps/ 등 불필요한 트리가 컨텍스트에 포함되면 전송 크기만 커집니다.
